  <section name="Guice configure Apache James Server">

    <p>Guice packaging ships additional features compared to Spring.</p>

    <p>
      For instance Guice allows you <a href="config-listeners.html">register additional mailbox listener</a>, allowing you to react to events generated by a user via MDA protocols IMAP or
      JMAP.
    </p>
    <p>
      In Cassandra Guice wiring, you can limit <a href="config-batchsizes.html">batch sizes</a>,
      in order to avoid overwhelming the database.
    </p>

  </section>

